title: Realistic in a very funny scenario
review: A very funny thematic movie about a realist what it can be like to get wild and drunk that can lead you to a very brain damaged hangover which could cause amnesia. to has been over a decade since this movie came out, and this is still very funny.

title: The Best dramatization about the Band
review: Rami Malek did an absolutely great job of portraying Freddie Mercury. that even his moves and his singing where exactly like his. The Song was a great hit, and the movie itself is a great hit. Nice 2 titles.
